Make sure it's an unsharpened pencil, you don't want the pencil lead to
break off in the combusion chamber.

Alternatively, use a plastic drinking straw (cold engine only) to help find
TDC.

> You can use a pencil in the spark plug hole
>to help make sure. This is TDC.
